!iflang [english]

!begin_node Cookie, WfNa

(!B)WFNAME.PRG(!b)

This extends MagiC by a special function which allows other programs 
to inquire the window title of any window.

For programmers:
!begin_itemize
!item As long as WFNAME.PRG is (!nolink [installed]), one can inquire window titles 
of any desired window with wind_get(WF_NAME).

!item  WFNAME.PRG can be recognized by a 'WfNa' cookie. A query whether 
  wind_get(WF_NAME) is possible should therefore be made as follows:

  'WfNa'-cookie present OR (!nl)
  'AmAN'-cookie present OR (!nl)
  MagiC >= 6.0 present.
!end_itemize

!end_node

!else

!begin_node Cookie, WfNa

